    <h2>What are cookies</h2>
    <p>Cookies are small text files that visited websites send to the browser, where they are stored and then retransmitted to the same sites on subsequent visits. They help sites work efficiently, remember user preferences, and — with consent — collect statistical data about visits.</p>

    <h2>Cookies used by this site</h2>

    <h3>Essential cookies (always active)</h3>
    <p>These cookies are strictly necessary for the website to function. They do not require consent and cannot be disabled.</p>

