    <h2>Self-hosted fonts and resources</h2>
    <p>The fonts used on this site (Playfair Display, Source Serif 4, DM Mono) are hosted directly on our servers and are <strong>not</strong> loaded from Google Fonts or any other third-party service. No data is transmitted to Google for font loading.</p>

    <h2>How to manage or withdraw consent</h2>
    <p>You can change your cookie preferences at any time:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="window.CookieConsent && window.CookieConsent.reset()"><strong>Click here to change your cookie preferences</strong></a></li>
    </ul>
    <p>You can also manage cookies directly from your browser settings. Note that disabling all cookies may affect the functionality of some websites.</p>

    <h2>No third-party advertising cookies</h2>
    <p>This site does <strong>not</strong> use social network cookies, advertising cookies, remarketing cookies or any other third-party profiling cookies.</p>

    <h2>Changes to this Cookie Policy</h2>
    <p>We reserve the right to modify this Cookie Policy at any time. Changes will be indicated by updating the date at the top of the page.</p>

